settings.clientNotes: Synthetic dataset generated for stress-testing the Audit-Ready Console. Replace with real data when ready.

checklist.title: Separate business bank account
checklist.desc: No mixed personal spending; if it exists, label it clearly.

checklist.title: Bank deposits reconciled monthly
checklist.desc: Every deposit tied to an invoice/payment or sales entry.

checklist.title: Invoices tracked (if invoicing)
checklist.desc: Invoice #, issue, due, amount, status, paid date + ref.

checklist.title: Receipts/records for expenses
checklist.desc: Receipts or invoices for major expenses; consistent categorization.

checklist.title: COGS vs OpEx separated
checklist.desc: Delivery costs vs overhead so margins are explainable.

checklist.title: Monthly P&L produced
checklist.desc: At least 12 months is ideal; no missing months.

checklist.title: Tax and payroll records organized
checklist.desc: W-9s/invoices for contractors; payroll reports if applicable.

checklist.title: Customer concentration noted
checklist.desc: If one client is >25% revenue, document it and mitigation plan.

checklist.title: Refunds/chargebacks logged
checklist.desc: Refunds/chargebacks recorded so revenue is clean.

checklist.title: Consistency narrative ready
checklist.desc: Explain seasonal spikes, promos, large one-offs, and trends.
